title: Silencer 1.0.apk
description:
This is an Android app developed by me. It can change ringer mode to silent or vibrate for a specified amount of time. It can also start when the silent or vibrate mode is changed(check the settings).

THIS DOES HAVE ADS. However, if anyone wants to use it, let me know in the comments and I will upload the ad free apk.

Basically, I just want to get some feedback whether the app works on others' devices, and what other improvements can be done. Thanks.

Permissions Explained -

Internet Access - Only for the ads

Start at boot - To ensure app works even after reboot. Doesn't mean that the app will start at boot
